OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Foccasional outbreaks of mainly light
OL,7,Frain or drizzle. Mostly dry and
OL,8,Fbrighter by the afternoon, however one
OL,9,For two isolated showers remain
OL,10,Fpossible. Becoming breezy, with gusty
OL,11,Fwinds offsetting the warmer
OL,12,Ftemperatures slightly.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FWidely dry and bright this
OL,15,Fevening, although still rather breezy.
OL,16,FLargely fine overnight with mostly
OL,17,Fclear skies, although clouding over
OL,18,Faround dawn, with the odd shower
OL,19,Fpossible in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
