OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FBright or sunny spells
OL,6,Fdeveloping with isolated showers on
OL,7,FSaturday. Breezy and feeling rather
OL,8,Fcool again.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,11,FGenerally dry with plenty of fine,
OL,12,Fbright weather expected. Rather cool
OL,13,Fand breezy on Sunday, but turning
OL,14,Fslightly warmer with lighter winds on
OL,15,FMonday and Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
